# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Liabilities Total Adjusted Amount

## identifier
de4931

## type
float

## definition
Report the total liabilities, adjusted for the prescribed yield change in the discount rate used in their valuation, in accordance with the capital adequacy standard.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.LiabilitiesTotalAdjusted.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
